from dateutil.relativedelta import relativedelta
import datetime

def compute_time_difference(DateTime1, DateTime2):
    """"""
    delta = relativedelta(DateTime1, DateTime2)
    years = delta.years
    months = delta.months
    days = delta.days
    hours = delta.hours
    minutes = delta.minutes
    return (years, months, days, hours, minutes)
